cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with deep learning techniques for segmentation tasks in the medical imaging domain, which is a common application area for computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also focuses on semi-supervised learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The authors use consistency targets to improve the performance of their model, which is a technique commonly used in neural network optimization (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with a specific type of dataset (MRI), which falls under the subcategory of multimedia (cs.MM).
